Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:13.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}My name's Kogorō Mouri... a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.61,0:00:17.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}Right... My job is to find people's faults.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:25.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Most all detectives have their own secret watering hole, for when they need to heal their work-weary hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:27.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.29,0:00:31.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This bar filled with youngsters loudly playing billiards and darts...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}is unfortunately not my preferred watering hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.47,0:00:38.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But my client happens to be the bartender here, so I must be here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.39,0:00:44.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you go, detective. Why don't you give this a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:49.61,Signs,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki Fukui (26)\NBartender
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:49.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}Her name is Yuzuki Fukui, 26. She's the bartender here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:52.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And she's probably fallen in love with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:59.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Giving me this faint green gimlet on the house is proof of her feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:06.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She must see that famous detective, Philip Marlowe in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:10.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is just green tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.96,0:01:14.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I thought you wouldn't be able to work if you were drunk...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:14.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:17.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No, wait... Let's start this over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.85,0:01:21.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}My name's Kogorō Mouri... a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.27,0:01:26.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}My client is the bartender of this billiard bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.52,0:01:31.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Here, my heart is soothed by lending my ear to this bar's off-beat jazz rhythms...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:33.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.23,0:01:34.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and this brat's voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:40.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are {\i1}you{\i0} here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.49,0:01:45.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r} told me to hurry up and get you, dinner's getting cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:48.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I told her, I'm here for a job!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:51.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which she said was probably just your excuse to have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.55,0:01:55.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You called me here to solve a difficult case, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:56.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:01:57.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:01:58.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What sort of case?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.47,0:02:01.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been hearing a strange sound while working.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:05.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A ‘pop', like a cork being pulled from a champagne bottle...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:10.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A sound like a cork being pulled from a champagne bottle...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:27.54,BCPrologue,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,0)}Only the light of deductions can tear apart the pitch-black shadows and bottomless darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:31.54,BCPrologue,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A case turns up over drinks at the Blue Parrot billiard bar! {This sounds a bit weird - maybe you can turn it into sth. better?}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:33.29,BCPrologue,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:35.30,BCPrologue,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.88,BCPrologue,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:06.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There you go, that sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:11.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it really was someone pulling a cork from a champagne bottle...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:16.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I heard it when nobody had a champagne bottle...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:20.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe a patron secretly brought in a bottle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:22.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And wine bottles have corks too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:27.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought the same thing, so I made sure to pay attention to all the patrons,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:31.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but none of them were drinking champagne or wine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:35.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And after I heard the pop, I also thought I heard something falling,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:41.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I looked around when cleaning up after the bar had closed, but couldn't find any corks lying around...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:44.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there was an odd scent...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:45.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An odd scent?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:50.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you could smell gunpowder, like something had exploded?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, nothing like that... I could smell {\i1}yuzu{\i0}.{TL Note: Chinese lemon}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:56.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was very faint,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:05:01.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but my name even has ‘yuzu' in it, so it's a smell I've always been quick to recognise...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:05:01.94,Signs,,0,0,0,,YUZU
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:05:01.94,Signs,,0,0,0,,KI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.49,0:05:09.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't use {\i1}yuzu{\i0} at this bar, so I thought it strange and decided to contact you, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:13.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe a patron had spilt a cocktail with a similar citrus fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:17.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, gimlets use lime juice,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:19.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and there's cocktails like screwdrivers and white ladies too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.47,0:05:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was sure it was {\i1}yuzu{\i0}, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:26.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you heard that sound more than once?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:29.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Two or three times, all on separate days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.56,0:05:33.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were there any patrons that were always here when you heard it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:34.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:39.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The four at the table behind you right now were always here at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:41.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm going to take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:43.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ready, say cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:48.37,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Boss, this roll of film's full up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:49.80,Signs,,0,0,0,,Mompei Kogure (28)\NEmployee
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.37,0:05:53.42,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, it's fine. I've got two or three spare rolls somewhere here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:56.29,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,And we've got plenty of extras now too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.14,0:05:55.56,Signs,,0,0,0,,Chikafumi Usuda (51)\NDepartment Head
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:57.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:59.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:01.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, Kogure{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.{AO}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:02.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:07.64,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kensaku Hatsumura (31)\NEmployee
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:07.64,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,But boss, don't you think analogue cameras are too much work these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:11.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate all that digital stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:15.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know... You remember that guy in our department?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:20.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That useless geek who always boasted that he was good with digital stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:22.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean Yoshikuwa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:27.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Yoshikuwa, Yoshikuwa... People like that get lost in their digital world and lose their grip on reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.91,0:06:34.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They become shut-ins and end up hanging themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:40.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, weren't you close to him, Kishiura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:46.09,Signs,,0,0,0,,Mika Kishiura (30)\NEmployee
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:46.09,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,If you're feeling lonely because you don't have a boyfriend, I could do something about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:48.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:53.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, give it a try! We'd be perfect for—{one another...}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:54.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh right, boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Hatsumura?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:07:01.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bought that billiard cue you asked for!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:05.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a top of the range cue with an ebony base, I found somewhere selling it at a discount.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:09.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. Thanks, Hatsumura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:12.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the best gift I could hope for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:13.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,G-G-Gift?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:18.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This {\i1}is{\i0} my birthday present, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:20.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got that personal darts set you wanted too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:33.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You usually see soft darts with plastic tips everywhere, so these fully metal darts were pretty hard to find...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:34.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That so, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:37.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys aren't so useless after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:42.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Obviously, they're a present for you too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:48.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogure! You know why I wanted steel-tipped darts?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:49.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:08:02.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plastic ones just don't scare people like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:09.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... Looks like a billiard table opened up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:15.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel like trying out this new cue you gave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:22.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, hurry off home and tell Ran this:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:28.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,‘Uncle Kogorō's working on a difficult case, so he won't be back for a while.'
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.78,0:08:32.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So there we go, Yuzuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}! Gimme a gimlet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:35.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But will you really be able to work if you're drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:38.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine, fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:40.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't blame me when this blows up in your face.{I can't be held responsible for how this turns out.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:49.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Uncle! Come home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:51.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}'s getting really mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:54.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmph, be quiet. You shouldn't have come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:56.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you, I'm working!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:08:59.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Looks more like you're just drinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:03.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, one more gimlet please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:06.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, you should be thinking about the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:11.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to put the solution on my blog when you figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:14.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I've just about solved it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:16.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.87,0:09:17.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:22.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit probably spilt some {\i1}ponzu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:23.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Made with {\i1}yuzu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:26.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ponzu{\i0} made with {\i1}yuzu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:27.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:30.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:32.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:36.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means there's ‘{\i1}yuzu{\i0}' and ‘{\i1}pon{\i0}'.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:39.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}pon
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yuzu{\i0} and a ‘pop'! Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:43.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's got the pop and all, see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:44.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's utterly hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:52.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the end, the boss passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:57.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He just keeps drinking, even though he can't hold his liquor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:09:58.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, it really stings...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:03.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That billiard cue cost me 100,000 yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:07.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The darts I bought cost 60,000 yen together with the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:11.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got off lightly, Kishiura. You just had to get five or six rolls of film, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:18.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you, he made me buy that poster of an idol on an online auction for a birthday present!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:21.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, you gave it to him back at the office...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:23.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's signed, so it cost me 30,000 yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.73,0:10:25.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mind if I take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:29.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just don't damage it. I'll be taking the blame if you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:31.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:34.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh, it's Yōko Okino...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.74,0:10:38.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then should we have one last round of drinks before we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:39.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:43.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were diluting and mixing up the whisky, and didn't end up drinking that much, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:45.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:48.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel like this ice pick's hardly left my hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:52.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then how about another bottle of champagne, finish like we started?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:53.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:55.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was very nice. What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:57.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:11:00.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me! A bottle of champagne, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:01.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coming up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:03.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, and three glasses too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:06.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Isn't that Kogorō Mouri sitting at the counter there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way! The great detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:13.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I feel like I'm being watched...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:15.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should get a photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:17.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it just someone who looks like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:19.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. He wouldn't be such a drunkard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:27.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really no good at getting these things out...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't point it at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:33.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogure{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, can you help?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:36.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogure's the best one to ask when you need some strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:38.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:43.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with this? It's really tight...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.77,0:11:46.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't have it fly off at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:48.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:54.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's spilling out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:58.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot! It's getting on the poster!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:12:00.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that's the sound I heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:02.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that was just champagne too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:04.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The side of the poster's wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:06.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:09.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me! Three hand towels please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:10.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:21.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about the sound of opening those hand towel packets?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:25.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could that have been the sound you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:31.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think the sound of the cork from before was closer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:36.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! The boss got soaked too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:38.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:39.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:42.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a round, red mark on his neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:44.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:48.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait... T-The boss isn't breathing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:50.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:54.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boss! Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:00.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:02.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:04.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:07.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our boss won't wake up, it's like he's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.77,0:13:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:14.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he doesn't just look dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:17.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He really is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:30.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}My name's Kogorō Mouri... a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:37.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I came to this billiard bar at the request of Yuzuki Fukui{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-chan{\r\be10}, the bartender here who's fallen for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:44.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But it seems that murders love me even more than she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:53.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't be sure without a proper autopsy, but I believe the cause of death was suffocation by a neurotoxin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:54.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,P-Poison?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:58.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. From the wound at the back of his neck,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:02.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it seems he was stabbed with something sharp like an awl, that had been coated with poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But wouldn't you usually yell out and make a scene if you were stabbed by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:11.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe he died in his sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:15.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim was dead drunk at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, you again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:18.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right you are, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:22.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you just {\i1}happened{\i0} to be at yet another murder scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:25.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah... I just happened to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:29.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes... A detective has a duty of confidentiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:33.06,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No matter what happens, he must never tell others about his clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:39.27,Thoughts,,10,10,0,,{\be10}To ensure suspicion never falls on Yuzuki{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-chan{\r\be10}, he must never mention that she hired him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:41.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His pride as a detective depends on it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:43.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I called him here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:47.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a mystery I wanted him to solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:48.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A mystery?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:54.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been hearing a ‘pop' sound while working here. It's the sound of a cork being pulled from a champagne bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:15:05.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, there aren't any patrons with champagne when it happens, and I didn't find a cork while cleaning up after closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:08.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I could smell the scent of {\i1}yuzu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:11.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, just how much is she paying you for this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:14.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said she'd clear off my tab...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:19.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, you'll still have to pay for the gimlets you drank tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.49,0:15:20.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:22.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:27.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those three were drinking with the victim, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:28.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:33.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I questioned each of them before you arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:35.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the right, they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mika Kishiura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:41.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kensaku Hatsumura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, 31.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:45.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Mompei Kogura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, 28.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.05,0:15:50.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They all worked at the same company as the murdered Usuda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, their boss,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:55.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and were apparently here tonight to celebrate his birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:16:05.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So one of these three resented and poisoned their supervisor...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:06.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,J-Just hold on a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:10.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We just came here to celebrate his birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:11.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We didn't poison him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:15.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You all planned this together, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:19.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were glancing round at me and talking amongst yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:23.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were talking about how you looked just like the famous Sleeping Kogorō.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.13,0:16:26.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who would've thought you were the real thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:29.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we don't even have any reason to kill him!{bullshit}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:35.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, you know, after your boss passed out, you got talking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:40.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You all said he forced you to get really expensive birthday presents and you were fed up with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You heard all that, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:46.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I've got good hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:55.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also heard him making fun of a guy named Yoshikuwa, who committed suicide, and that you and Yoshikuwa were lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:16:57.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, he's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:04.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you're bringing that up, Hatsumura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was his senior at university too,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:07.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and he joined the company together with Kogure{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:12.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we hated him enough to kill him, we wouldn't have played billiards and darts with him in the first place, would we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:14.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You played games with the victim?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:19.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We each took turns playing him until he passed out...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:25.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, did their boss really play games with those three?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:29.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, you went home several times, so you didn't see what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:32.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Their boss was making a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:35.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dartboard here is designed for soft darts,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:40.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he tried to use the steel-tipped darts he was given,\Nand ended up arguing with the other patrons...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:44.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those three had to step in, and managed to cool him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:50.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seemed like they told him to wait at the table until he sobered up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:52.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then what happened after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:58.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The three of them played billiards and darts amongst themselves for a while, winner-stays-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:05.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then while two of them were playing, the other one of the three was all alone with their drunken boss, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:13.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, all three of you were alone with your boss at some point...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:18.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we'll need to perform body searches and check your belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:23.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A billiard cue...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:26.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It does look expensive...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It was supposed to be 160,000 yen.\NI got it because it was reduced to 100,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.55,0:18:41.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Of course, just like that kid overheard, I was annoyed since I never intended for something so expensive to be a present...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:44.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But do you really think I'd kill him, just for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:53.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But... If you stuck a poisoned needle to the tip of the cue with some tape, then you'd even be able to stab him from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:58.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I'd done something that weird, someone would've seen it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:19:00.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I didn't, did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:01.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:06.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After their boss passed out, he put it straight in its case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:13.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so these are the dart tips that caused the argument...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:17.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't buy them to cause an argument!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:20.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The boss told me to buy him steel-tipped darts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:27.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My late grandfather left me an antique dartboard, so I gave it to our boss, and he told me to go buy darts to go with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.98,0:19:30.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't even play darts...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:36.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, you got quite the fright when your boss feigned throwing a dart at you, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:42.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that was really scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:47.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you have stuck poison on the end of one of the darts, and thrown it at him to stab him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:50.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just told you, I'm no good with darts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:56.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even if I wanted to, it'd be simpler and easier to just have stabbed him with them from up close...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:57.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:20:01.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you suspect me, then just check out the tips of those darts, and you'll see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:04.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, we intend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:10.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got him some rolls of film and a poster of an idol?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:14.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It does seem you got off easy compared to the other two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:18.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on! That poster's signed, it cost me 30,000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.99,0:20:25.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My desk's next to his desk, so I had to listen to him always telling me how much he wanted it and I had to buy it for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:31.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can smell something from the wet part of the poster...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:34.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is that... {\i1}yuzu{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:37.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:38.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So the old man realised it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:41.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a poster of Yōko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:44.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's the elusive western bikini shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:45.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10\i1}Is {\i1}that{\i0} what he noticed...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:47.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you got it wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:49.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}bijo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:49.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}bijo-bijo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:49.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The pretty lady's pretty soaked because of you!{oh geez, not THAT pun}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:50.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And he's making bad jokes too...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:55.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The champagne spilt out when Kogure{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} pulled out the cork.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:21:00.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You seem to have taken quite a lot of photos too...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:02.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did your boss like photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.24,0:21:06.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. They were for his blog.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:11.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so, we're the ones who have to choose and upload them...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:13.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The boss was hopeless with anything digital.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:17.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet he wanted to seem cool by having a blog...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:22.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess at least after everything that's happened, we won't have to pick out photos to use too...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:27.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! That's hardly a reason why we'd want to kill him, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:31.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, who was in charge of mixing up and diluting the whisky?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:34.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was me, but why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:37.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we'll have to check this out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:45.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ice pick is sharp and pointed too, just like the tips of the darts. It's very close to the shape of the murder weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:54.16,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}My name's Kogorō Mouri... a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:22:03.17,Thoughts,,10,10,0,,{\be10}It seems my essence as a detective has brought disaster through the doors of this billiard bar, a place of refreshment...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:05.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.38,0:22:10.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I guess I'm going to have another sleepless night over a case...
